Jo Van Fleet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jo_Van_Fleet 0 Catherine Josephine Van Fleet (December 29, 1915 – June 10, 1996) was a theatre, film, and television actress from the United States. Known primarily for playing roles older than she was, her career spanned over three decades, and she won an Academy Award as well as a Tony Award.
